      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="praying over-header"> Download Concrn for a helping hand when it's needed most. Submit a detailed report to a local agency in under a minute. Friendly, trained responders will arrive on scene to provide care. And it's all free.</div>
        <div class="praying heading">How Concrn works</div>
      </div>
