          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <img src="/assets/home/concrn-ios.png"/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center" style="float: right;">
          <p class="praying copy">
           Concrn's pilot partnership is with the <br><a href="http://www.downtownrangers.com">Las Vegas Downtown Rangers</a>! <br>Use Concrn in Downtown Las Vegas to get help from an amazing Ranger.
          </p>
          <p class="praying copy">
           Use Concrn to create reports even when there isn't an agency in your area! The more reports submitted the easier it is to show local government and non-profits the need for compassionate response. Tell your family, friends, and co-workers!
          </p>
          <p class="praying copy">
           Interested in getting involved with Concrn?<br><a href="mailto:info@concrn.com">Contact us </a>to find out how Concrn can empower your community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
